00:29:10,457 --> 00:29:12,917
One, two, three, good.

391
00:29:13,585 --> 00:29:15,003
Get back up. As you were.

392
00:29:15,295 --> 00:29:17,881
Attention. Bow to Mr. Nam.

393
00:29:19,507 --> 00:29:20,842
GENTLENESS DOMINATES STRENGTH

394
00:29:23,470 --> 00:29:24,554
It's strange.

395
00:29:25,472 --> 00:29:28,683
Before I had a child,
I never liked children.

396
00:29:29,768 --> 00:29:31,895
But my baby is so adorable.

397
00:29:32,520 --> 00:29:35,315
I don't know if I became my kid's fangirl
because of my fangirling experience,

398
00:29:35,398 --> 00:29:38,818
or it's because
I can't be a fangirl anymore.

399
00:29:40,862 --> 00:29:41,946
Seon-ju.

400
00:29:42,822 --> 00:29:44,741
-Why did you get married?
-Because I had Geon-u.

401
00:29:44,824 --> 00:29:48,161
No. I mean how did you
start dating Seung-min?

402
00:29:48,244 --> 00:29:49,329
Instead of an idol star.

403
00:29:51,581 --> 00:29:53,583
I somehow fell for him.

404
00:29:54,167 --> 00:29:55,710
-Although he wasn't an idol star?
-Yes.

405
00:29:56,461 --> 00:29:58,963
When I liked idol stars,

406
00:29:59,047 --> 00:30:01,424
they were my boyfriends,
and when I was dating,

407
00:30:02,050 --> 00:30:03,927
my boyfriend was my idol star.

408
00:30:06,095 --> 00:30:07,847
That was how I felt back then.

409
00:30:09,808 --> 00:30:11,226
Will Duk-mi be like that too?

410
00:30:12,644 --> 00:30:13,728
Will Duk-mi somehow

411
00:30:15,438 --> 00:30:16,815
fall for a guy like that?

412
00:30:17,941 --> 00:30:19,567
-Not an idol star, but--
-You mean Lion?

413
00:30:21,402 --> 00:30:22,529
Does it bother you?

414
00:30:23,363 --> 00:30:24,948
That Duk-mi might like Lion?

415
00:30:26,616 --> 00:30:28,409
What are you talking about?

416
00:30:29,744 --> 00:30:31,871
Kids, you shouldn't fight!

417
00:30:32,455 --> 00:30:35,458
Don't fight.
Don't fight and go play with this!

418
00:30:36,626 --> 00:30:38,586
Eun-gi, you idiot.

419
00:30:39,546 --> 00:30:41,965
You're the most dull-witted person
in the world.

420
00:30:46,094 --> 00:30:47,095
Geon-u.

421
00:30:49,681 --> 00:30:50,598
It's Mom.

422
00:30:51,432 --> 00:30:53,893
I brought some more. Good.

423
00:30:58,731 --> 00:31:01,734
Mr. Kim. From now on,
if you plan to visit here,

424
00:31:01,818 --> 00:31:04,028
please report to me
at least three hours in advance.

425
00:31:04,571 --> 00:31:06,865
I hope you wouldn't barge in like this
without prior notice

426
00:31:06,948 --> 00:31:08,366
ever again.

427
00:31:11,661 --> 00:31:14,622
I'm Eom So-hye.

428
00:31:15,081 --> 00:31:17,333
Do you mean I need permission

429
00:31:17,417 --> 00:31:19,252
to visit my own museum?

430
00:31:20,461 --> 00:31:23,214
Do you confess to the privatization
of this museum then?

431
00:31:25,550 --> 00:31:27,468
How could you say that?

432
00:31:27,594 --> 00:31:29,596
I hate words such as confession,
interrogation, or arrest.

433
00:31:29,679 --> 00:31:31,431
I seriously detest them.

434
00:31:32,682 --> 00:31:35,226
Director Eom, we're in the middle
of a meeting right now.

435
00:31:37,145 --> 00:31:39,272
I'm very busy too.

436
00:31:39,939 --> 00:31:42,817
I have to prepare snacks
for Hyo-jin myself,

437
00:31:43,318 --> 00:31:45,612
and I also have to bring food
for my husband

438
00:31:45,695 --> 00:31:48,031
in prison due to his picky taste.

439
00:31:49,282 --> 00:31:50,575
It's so tiring.

440
00:31:51,951 --> 00:31:52,994
Ms. Sung.

441
00:31:54,329 --> 00:31:56,414
What are you doing next week
when the museum is closed?

442
00:31:57,165 --> 00:32:00,919
Next week is when Si-an is holding
his signing event.

443
00:32:02,378 --> 00:32:03,546
Why do you ask that?

444
00:32:03,630 --> 00:32:07,550
I've made some new friends recently.

445
00:32:08,009 --> 00:32:10,261
It's called W.R.E.O.

446
00:32:10,678 --> 00:32:12,722
It means, Wives of Righteous

447
00:32:12,805 --> 00:32:14,474
Economic Offenders.

448
00:32:14,557 --> 00:32:16,309
W.R.E.O.

449
00:32:16,768 --> 00:32:19,312
They said they would like
to take a quiet and private tour

450
00:32:19,395 --> 00:32:20,897
of our museum.

451
00:32:21,105 --> 00:32:23,650
Ms. Sung, please be the docent
of that tour.

452
00:32:23,983 --> 00:32:25,026
Can you do it?

453
00:32:30,698 --> 00:32:31,741
Yes, ma'am.

454
00:32:33,284 --> 00:32:34,661
Then I'll see you next Monday.

455
00:32:34,786 --> 00:32:35,745
Ms. Sung

456
00:32:36,245 --> 00:32:37,747
doesn't have time on that day.

457
00:32:38,289 --> 00:32:41,417
If they want a quiet tour, tell them
to come in the morning when it opens.

458
00:32:44,212 --> 00:32:45,588
Do you two have a date?

459
00:32:45,755 --> 00:32:48,758
This is why it's bad
to date someone at work.

460
00:32:49,384 --> 00:32:51,177
You're totally messing up the mood.

461
00:32:51,260 --> 00:32:52,929
I'm glad you can read the room.

462
00:32:53,888 --> 00:32:56,140
Think carefully about
who is messing up the mood now.

463
00:32:56,557 --> 00:33:00,019
Are you mad? Are you worried
that you won't get to go on a date?

464
00:33:01,020 --> 00:33:04,357
Director Gold has a meeting
with Mr. Cha Si-an that day.

465
00:33:04,440 --> 00:33:05,900
It's a business matter.

466
00:33:07,026 --> 00:33:07,986
Really?

467
00:33:10,738 --> 00:33:13,700
I'd like to participate
in various types of work too.

468
00:33:13,783 --> 00:33:15,618
May I participate in that meeting too?

469
00:33:16,244 --> 00:33:17,161
Hyo-jin?

470
00:33:17,870 --> 00:33:18,871
Ms. Kim.

471
00:33:19,330 --> 00:33:20,581
Are you free that day?

472
00:33:20,873 --> 00:33:21,791
Yes.

473
00:33:23,626 --> 00:33:24,669
I'm glad.

474
00:33:25,795 --> 00:33:29,048
Ms. Kim will be the docent
for the private tour then.

475
00:33:30,008 --> 00:33:33,344
For her mother and the members of W.R.E.O.

476
00:33:34,429 --> 00:33:35,596
Director Gold!

477
00:33:35,680 --> 00:33:36,764
Hyo-jin?

478
00:33:37,390 --> 00:33:39,058
Can you be the docent?

479
00:33:40,226 --> 00:33:42,311
That will make me so happy.

480
00:33:42,395 --> 00:33:44,772
You must make me feel proud.

481
00:33:45,064 --> 00:33:46,149
I'm so glad.

482
00:33:46,232 --> 00:33:47,817
-Mom.
-Have a good day then.

483
00:33:47,900 --> 00:33:49,694
-It turns out I have plans that day!
-Bye.

484
00:33:49,777 --> 00:33:52,864
-Mom.
-I feel so happy right now.

485
00:33:53,489 --> 00:33:54,782
She's so hilarious.

486
00:33:59,829 --> 00:34:01,372
Thank you, Director Gold.

487
00:34:02,832 --> 00:34:04,500
Don't worry about it, Ms. Sung.

488
00:34:12,508 --> 00:34:14,343
So, Cha Si-an

489
00:34:14,427 --> 00:34:17,180
has three pieces by Lee Sol.

490
00:34:17,555 --> 00:34:19,724
Next, if we include Mr. Roh Seok,

491
00:34:19,807 --> 00:34:22,226
that will total up to 31 pieces.

492
00:34:22,310 --> 00:34:23,686
Did you measure the sizes?

493
00:34:24,103 --> 00:34:27,440
Director Gold told me to measure the sizes
after signing the contract.

494
00:34:28,816 --> 00:34:32,070
Didn't Director Gold sound
so cool earlier?

495
00:34:32,153 --> 00:34:33,154
Earlier?

496
00:34:34,697 --> 00:34:35,865
-When?
-Earlier.

497
00:34:35,948 --> 00:34:38,451
When he stood up
against Director Eom during the meeting.

498
00:34:39,243 --> 00:34:41,788
Do you find that cool? I'm not sure.

499
00:34:42,038 --> 00:34:44,165
Director Gold and Ms. Sung act like

500
00:34:44,248 --> 00:34:45,958
they're not dating at all usually,

501
00:34:46,042 --> 00:34:49,253
but when he sided with her
at that moment, it looked so cool.

502
00:34:49,420 --> 00:34:50,922
I'm not sure.

503
00:34:51,547 --> 00:34:52,507
What...

504
00:34:54,383 --> 00:34:55,760
What did you just say?

505
00:34:59,806 --> 00:35:03,351
It's not settled yet, but five
to seven collectors will be participating,

506
00:35:03,434 --> 00:35:06,437
and we're expecting
about 50 pieces of artwork.

507
00:35:06,604 --> 00:35:07,897
The most important thing is

508
00:35:08,022 --> 00:35:10,483
categorizing the artwork and deciding
on the concept of the exhibition.

509
00:35:11,234 --> 00:35:14,237
